  "name": "multilingual-text-to-amr",
  "description": "Generating AMR (Abstract Meaning Representation) from text in multiple languages using MBART finetuned models. This comprehensive toolkit provides multilingual text-to-AMR parsing capabilities for English, Spanish, and Dutch, with advanced evaluation metrics including SMATCH and SMATCH++. The system includes configuration files for reproducing CLIN conference models, evaluation scripts, and support for distributed training with DeepSpeed.",
